Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:51.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}貴方を飾る晴る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:57.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}胸を打つ音よ凪げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:01.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}僕ら晴る風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:05.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}あの雲も越えてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:10.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}遠くまだ遠くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:57.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你就像风一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:01.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}闭上眼 已是黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:07.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:15.91,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}睁开双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:20.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}你的眼眸晶莹透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:27.34,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}散发着丝丝晴的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:38.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}晴空万里 花开遍地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:42.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}百花皆为晴而开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:47.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}就连初晴后的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:51.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}也是装饰于你的晴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:57.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}心中的悸动啊化作细风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:01.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我们亦化为晴风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:05.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}穿过那片云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:10.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直到天边
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:52.98,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}And I'm alright (I'll be alright)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:55.85,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Yeah I hear you (I care about you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.36,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}伸びた髪を風がからかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}全部意味があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.91,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}立ち止まった日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:13.33,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}今さらわかってあなたに追いついたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.33,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:20.21,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}見えなかったものが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:24.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}どうして？　溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:31.26,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}せめて　会いたいよなんて言わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:36.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}ねえ　今日だけは思い出していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:42.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}だから　あなたと　また巡り逢ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:48.82,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}もう迷わない　今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:54.50,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}どこにいても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.50,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}笑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:00.50,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}目を閉じれば　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.25,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}絶対なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:06.30,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}いつでも届いてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:12.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}その涙だって大丈夫　きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:19.44,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}I'm whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:52.98,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我还好 (我一切安好)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:55.85,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我听见你了 (我一直牵挂着你)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.36,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}微风轻拂飘浮的长发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.90,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}一切都有其意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.91,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}包括那些停滞的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:13.33,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如今我终于像你那般明白了这些道理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.33,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那些曾经只有这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:20.21,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}才能看见的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:24.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}为何如今已随处可见？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:31.26,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我不会再祈求与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:36.90,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以至少给我回忆今天的权利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:42.94,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以如果 还能与你相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:48.82,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那就不再迷茫 我还会选择当下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:54.50,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.50,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}让我看看你的笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:00.50,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}无论何时 只需闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.25,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不需要什么绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:06.30,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我们一直心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:12.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不必强忍泪水 黎明总会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:19.44,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我正哼着我们的摇篮曲 等你回家呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
